OL,3,CManchester surgeon receives MBE for
OL,4,Cuniting interfaith communities
OL,6,FDr Nasser Kurdy has been awarded an
OL,7,FMBE at Windsor Castle for services to
OL,8,Fcommunity interfaith reconciliation.
OL,10,FThe honour was given to Dr Kurdy by
OL,11,FThe Princess Royal at Windsor Castle.
OL,13,FDr Kurdy from Altrincham hosts The
OL,14,FRabbi, The Imam And The Power Of
OL,15,FDialogue podcast with Rabbi Dovid
OL,16,FLewis, alongside his work as a
OL,17,Fconsultant orthopaedic surgeon.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
