CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1781093477
OL,3,CManchester surgeon receives MBE for
OL,4,Cuniting interfaith communities
OL,6,FThe two have been friends for 13
OL,7,Fyears, and since 2018 have been co-
OL,8,Fhosting talks, volunteering sessions
OL,9,Fand religious ceremonies for their
OL,10,Frespective communities.
OL,12,FThey launched the podcast in May 2025,
OL,13,Fprompted by the turmoil between their
OL,14,Fcommunities, evident since Hamas's
OL,15,Fattack on Israel on October 7 2023.
OL,16,FThe pair take their talks of unity
OL,17,Finto schools.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
