OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1781093477
OL,3,CManchester surgeon receives MBE for
OL,4,Cuniting interfaith communities
OL,6,FDr Kurdy, who was born in Syria and
OL,7,Fhas Jordanian heritage, said that the
OL,8,FMBE award represented more work to do
OL,9,Fbetween the communities.
OL,11,FHe said "It's amazing, and it's also
OL,12,Fsad in a way. I don't like to be
OL,13,Frecognised for trying to get people
OL,14,Ftogether because you'd like people to
OL,15,Fhave never been apart."
OL,26,@sD@IOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,394,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1781093477
OL,3,CManchester surgeon receives MBE for
OL,4,Cuniting interfaith communities
OL,6,F"I suppose it's inevitable people will
OL,7,Ffall out with each other, but when
OL,8,Fit's on such a grand scale and when
OL,9,Fthe narrative on both sides is so
OL,10,Fentrenched and negative you just can't
OL,11,Fsee any glimmer of light shining
OL,12,Fthrough and that's been the difficult
OL,13,Fpart of it."
OL,15,F"It's not just the (Heaton Park)
OL,16,Fsynagogue attack, there was the madman
OL,17,Fin Golders Green and Bondi Beach,
OL,18,Fwhere Rabbi Dovid's cousin was killed,
OL,19,Fso it's never far away from you."
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
