PN,39305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1781093477
OL,3,CManchester surgeon receives MBE for
OL,4,Cuniting interfaith communities
OL,6,F"They cause anxiety and entrench
OL,7,Fdivisions."
OL,9,F"But you can't allow for that and
OL,10,Fthere should be no division in our
OL,11,Fsociety."
OL,13,F"It's amazing that 5% of darkness can
OL,14,Factually overshadow 95% of light."
OL,16,F"That is scary and for me and for
OL,17,FRabbi Dovid, we've decided we really
OL,18,Fhave to just knuckle down and tell
OL,19,Fpeople that Muslims and Jews are
OL,20,Fbrothers, they have to be there
OL,21,Ftogether.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@AOUuD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
