OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F393A1781093477
OL,3,CManchester surgeon receives MBE for
OL,4,Cuniting interfaith communities
OL,6,F"The response has been amazing.
OL,8,F"He sent me a message this morning
OL,9,Fsaying 'enjoy your day' ` he's been
OL,10,Fhaving congregants saying
OL,11,Fcongratulations to him but he didn't
OL,12,Fget one, I've been teasing him!"
OL,14,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,15,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,16,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,17,Four region.
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@AOUtD@`O]
